  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Flow 2 — Workflow Progress",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 7,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "\nFrontend operations for **workers polling** for work (`Poll*`) and **completing** it (`Respond*`).\nThis is the server side of worker activity — pair it with the **Worker Fleet & KEDA Scaling**\ndashboard for the SDK/worker view (slots, sticky cache, schedule-to-start).\n\n**Works on Cloud AND self-hosted OSS** — each panel carries an OSS target (`service_requests`/\n`service_latency`, rate-based) and a Cloud target (`temporal_cloud_v1_*`, precomputed rate/\npercentile); whichever backend you're running populates the panel.\n\n> **Caveat:** OSS `service_latency` for `Respond*` **includes** the time the worker is responsible\n> for, so treat the latency below as worker-inclusive. The persistence panel for this flow moved to\n> **Temporal Self-Hosted Internals — Server Health** (self-hosted only, permanently).\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Progress — Respond*",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 7
      },
      "id": 2,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Respond* RPS by Operation",
      "description": "OSS: service_requests (rate). Cloud: temporal_cloud_v1_service_request_count (precomputed rate, no rate()).",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus-kind"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 8
      },
      "id": 3,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus-kind"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (operation) (rate(service_requests{operation=~\"RespondWorkflowTaskCompleted|RespondActivityTaskCompleted|RespondWorkflowTaskFailed|RespondActivityTaskFailed|RespondActivityTaskCanceled\"}[$rate]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{operation}}"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus-kind"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (operation) (temporal_cloud_v1_service_request_count{operation=~\"RespondWorkflowTaskCompleted|RespondActivityTaskCompleted|RespondWorkflowTaskFailed|RespondActivityTaskFailed|RespondActivityTaskCanceled\"})",
          "legendFormat": "{{operation}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Respond* Errors by Operation",
      "description": "OSS: service_errors (rate). Cloud: temporal_cloud_v1_service_error_count (precomputed rate, no rate()).",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus-kind"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 8
      },
      "id": 4,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus-kind"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (operation) (rate(service_errors{operation=~\"RespondWorkflowTaskCompleted|RespondActivityTaskCompleted|RespondWorkflowTaskFailed|RespondActivityTaskFailed|RespondActivityTaskCanceled\"}[$rate]) OR on() vector(0))",
          "legendFormat": "{{operation}}"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus-kind"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (operation) (temporal_cloud_v1_service_error_count{operation=~\"RespondWorkflowTaskCompleted|RespondActivityTaskCompleted|RespondWorkflowTaskFailed|RespondActivityTaskFailed|RespondActivityTaskCanceled\"})",
          "legendFormat": "{{operation}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Respond* Latency p99 by Operation (incl. worker time)",
      "description": "OSS: histogram_quantile over service_latency_bucket. Cloud: temporal_cloud_v1_service_latency_p99 (already a percentile).",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus-kind"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 16
      },
      "id": 5,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus-kind"
          },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (operation, le) (rate(service_latency_bucket{operation=~\"RespondWorkflowTaskCompleted|RespondActivityTaskCompleted|RespondWorkflowTaskFailed|RespondActivityTaskFailed|RespondActivityTaskCanceled\"}[$rate])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{operation}}"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus-kind"
          },
          "expr": "max by (operation) (temporal_cloud_v1_service_latency_p99{operation=~\"RespondWorkflowTaskCompleted|RespondActivityTaskCompleted|RespondWorkflowTaskFailed|RespondActivityTaskFailed|RespondActivityTaskCanceled\"})",
          "legendFormat": "{{operation}}"
        }
      ]
    },
